Package: mongolite
Type: Package
Title: Streaming Mongo Client
Description: R bindings to the high-performance MongoDB C driver and
    high-level IO tools in the same spirit as jsonlite.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-03-27
Author: Jeroen Ooms, MongoDB Inc.
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Depends: methods, utils
Imports: jsonlite
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/jeroenooms/mongolite, https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver
BugReports: https://github.com/jeroenooms/mongolite/issues
SystemRequirements:
    OpenSSL: libssl-dev (deb) or openssl-devel (rpm),
    SASL: libsasl2-dev (deb) or cyrus-sasl-devel (rpm)
